<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>RiskLens Economic Signals</title>

<style>
*{
box-sizing:border-box;
margin:0;
padding:0;
}

:root{
--bg:#030712;
--panel:#081120;
--line:#163052;
--text:#eef6ff;
--muted:#9bb3d9;
--cyan:#00d4ff;
--yellow:#f5b942;
--orange:#ff8a3d;
--red:#ff4d6d;
--green:#19e68c;
}

body{
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
background:
radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(0,212,255,.10), transparent 22%),
radial-gradient(circle at 80% 10%, rgba(139,92,246,.12), transparent 25%),
linear-gradient(180deg,#030712,#07111f 45%,#040914);
color:var(--text);
overflow-x:hidden;
}

.topbar{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:18px 22px;
background:rgba(4,10,22,.78);
border-bottom:1px solid rgba(76,201,240,.18);
position:sticky;
top:0;
z-index:20;
}

.brand{
color:var(--cyan);
font-size:22px;
font-weight:bold;
}

.menu a{
color:#dcecff;
text-decoration:none;
margin-left:18px;
font-size:14px;
}

.container{
max-width:1200px;
margin:auto;
padding:34px 20px 60px;
}

.hero{
background:rgba(8,17,32,.78);
border:1px solid rgba(76,201,240,.16);
border-radius:20px;
padding:28px;
margin-bottom:24px;
box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(0,212,255,.06);
}

.hero h1{
font-size:40px;
color:var(--cyan);
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.hero p{
color:var(--muted);
line-height:1.8;
max-width:850px;
}

.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
gap:18px;
}

.card{
background:rgba(8,17,32,.78);
border:1px solid rgba(76,201,240,.14);
border-radius:18px;
padding:22px;
}

.label{
font-size:12px;
text-transform:uppercase;
letter-spacing:.05em;
color:var(--muted);
margin-bottom:8px;
}

.metric{
font-size:34px;
font-weight:bold;
color:var(--cyan);
}

.sub{
margin-top:10px;
font-size:13px;
color:#9db5dc;
line-height:1.7;
}

.band{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:10px;
padding:6px 10px;
border-radius:999px;
font-size:12px;
font-weight:bold;
text-transform:uppercase;
}

.low{
color:var(--green);
background:rgba(25,230,140,.12);
}
.medium{
color:var(--yellow);
background:rgba(245,185,66,.12);
}
.high{
color:var(--orange);
background:rgba(255,138,61,.12);
}
.critical{
color:var(--red);
background:rgba(255,77,109,.12);
}

.panel{
background:rgba(8,17,32,.78);
border:1px solid rgba(76,201,240,.14);
border-radius:18px;
padding:22px;
margin-top:20px;
}

.panel h2{
color:var(--cyan);
margin-bottom:12px;
}

.panel p, .panel li{
color:var(--muted);
line-height:1.8;
}

.panel ul{
padding-left:18px;
}

@media(max-width:1000px){
.grid{
grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
}
}

@media(max-width:700px){
.grid{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}
.hero h1{
font-size:32px;
}
.menu{
display:none;
}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="brand">RiskLens</div>
  <div class="menu">
    <a href="/risklens/dashboard.html">Dashboard</a>
    <a href="/risklens/advisor.html">Economic AI</a>
    <a href="/risklens/worldmap.html">Global Map</a>
    <a href="/risklens/sectors.html">Sectors</a>
    <a href="/risklens/crisis.html">Crisis</a>
    <a href="/risklens/signals.html">Signals</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Economic Signals</h1>
    <p>
      RiskLens monitors a compact set of macro and market signals to understand where pressure
      is building. These indicators help explain inflation regimes, financing conditions,
      commodity stress and broader market behavior.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">

    <div class="card">
      <div class="label">Inflation</div>
      <div class="metric">5.4%</div>
      <div class="band high">Elevated</div>
      <div class="sub">Persistent pricing pressure remains one of the main macro stress drivers.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="label">Interest Rate</div>
      <div class="metric">4.8%</div>
      <div class="band medium">Restrictive</div>
      <div class="sub">Higher rates tighten credit conditions and slow fragile demand segments.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="label">Oil</div>
      <div class="metric">$82</div>
      <div class="band medium">Watch</div>
      <div class="sub">Energy sensitivity still matters for transport, manufacturing and inflation.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="label">Gold</div>
      <div class="metric">$2,310</div>
      <div class="band low">Defensive</div>
      <div class="sub">Gold remains a defensive reference under uncertainty and inflation concerns.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="label">BTC</div>
      <div class="metric">$67,200</div>
      <div class="band high">Volatile</div>
      <div class="sub">Crypto markets continue to reflect liquidity cycles and speculative risk appetite.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="label">S&amp;P 500</div>
      <div class="metric">5,180</div>
      <div class="band medium">Mixed</div>
      <div class="sub">Equity resilience can weaken quickly when rates and earnings expectations diverge.</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Signal Interpretation</h2>
    <p>
      The current signal mix suggests moderate-to-elevated pressure: inflation remains sticky,
      interest rates stay restrictive and commodity sensitivity continues to affect economic
      transmission channels.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Why Signals Matter</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Inflation shapes purchasing power and cost structure.</li>
      <li>Interest rates change credit speed and investment appetite.</li>
      <li>Oil and commodities feed production and logistics stress.</li>
      <li>Gold and crypto often reflect defensive or speculative capital movement.</li>
      <li>Equity benchmarks summarize confidence and forward expectations.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
